    <h3>What data do we collect?</h3>
    <p>TCG Report App collects the following data:</p>
    <ul>
        <li>Crash logs.</li>
    </ul>
    <h3>How do we collect your data?</h3>    
    <p>In case you opted in to share your <a href="https://support.google.com/accounts/answer/6078260?sjid=13125954672581308857-EU">usage and diagnostic</a> 
        data with Google, TCG Report App may also receive your data indirectly from the following sources:</p>
    <ul>
        <li>Google Play Console.</li>
    </ul>
    <h3>How will we use your data?</h3>
    <p>TCG Report App collects your data so that we can:</p>
    <ul>
        <li>Inspect and analyze any crash logs you might share in order to fix issues and improve TCG Report App.</li>
    </ul>
    <h3>How do we store your data?</h3>
    <p>TCG Report App might keep your crash logs for up to 60 days. Once this time period has expired, crash logs
        will be automatically deleted (as Google Play Console's Android Vitals retention policy will have expired).</p>
    <h3>Marketing</h3>
    <p>TCG Report App won't send you information about products and services of ours that we think you might like,
        nor those of our partner companies.</p>
    <h3>What are your data protection rights?</h3>
    <p>TCG Report App would like to make sure you are fully aware of all of your data protection rights. Every user is
        entitled to the following:</p>
    <p><strong>The right to access</strong> – You have the right to request TCG Report App for copies of your personal
        data. We may charge you a small fee for this service.</p>
    <p><strong>The right to rectification</strong> – You have the right to request that TCG Report App correct any
        information you believe is inaccurate. You also have the right to request TCG Report App to complete the
        information you believe is incomplete.</p>
    <p><strong>The right to erasure</strong> – You have the right to request that TCG Report App erase your personal data,
        under certain conditions.</p>
    <p><strong>The right to restrict processing</strong> – You have the right to request that TCG Report App restrict the
        processing of your personal data, under certain conditions.</p>
    <p><strong>The right to object to processing</strong> – You have the right to object to TCG Report App's processing of
        your personal data, under certain conditions.</p>
    <p><strong>The right to data portability</strong> – You have the right to request that TCG Report App transfer the data
        that we have collected to another organization, or directly to you, under certain conditions.</p>
    <p>If you make a request, we have one month to respond to you. If you would like to exercise any of these rights,
        please contact us at our email <a href="mailto:german.coines@gmail.com?subject=TCG Report App - Data Protection Rights">german.coines@gmail.com</a> 
        with subject "TCG Report App - Data Protection Rights" and your request.</p>
